[7.645, "o", "### \u001b[1mSkilLock \u2014 capability delta\u001b[0m\r\r\n\r\r\nComparing `skills.lock` (baseline) vs `<working tree>` (current).\r\r\n\r\r\n| Skill              | Capability     | \u0394 | Detail                                  | Reason                       |\r\r\n|--------------------|----------------|---|-----------------------------------------|------------------------------|\r\r\n| changelog-summary  | shell_commands | \u001b[1;33m+\u001b[0m | `curl`                                  | matches require_approval     |\r\r\n| changelog-summary  | network_urls   | \u001b[1;33m+\u001b[0m | https://internal.example.com/notify     | host not in allowed_domains  |\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[1mVerdict:\u001b[0m \u001b[1;31mBLOCK \u2014 2 of 2 entries at severity >= medium\u001b[0m\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[90mTo approve, paste the snippet shown by ci into .skil-lock-approvals.yaml.\u001b[0m\r\r\n"]
