[16.15, "o", "\u001b[90mapproved: skill=changelog-summary reviewer=alice reason=\"release notify ping\"\u001b[0m\r\r\n\u001b[90mapproved: skill=changelog-summary reviewer=alice reason=\"release notify ping\"\u001b[0m\r\r\n### \u001b[1mSkilLock \u2014 no capability deltas\u001b[0m\r\r\n\r\r\nBaseline `skills.lock` matches current `<working tree>`.\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[1mVerdict:\u001b[0m \u001b[1;32mPASS \u2014 no capability deltas\u001b[0m\r\r\n"]
